WEBVTT

1
00:00:17.205 --> 00:00:21.333
- [screaming in pain]
- [Boyd] <i>Previously on</i> From...

2
00:00:21.334 --> 00:00:24.128
That thing I carried inside me.
I still feel it.

3
00:00:24.329 --> 00:00:26.080
[roars]

4
00:00:26.081 --> 00:00:28.123
Stop!

5
00:00:28.124 --> 00:00:29.583
I've connected with that thing.

6
00:00:29.584 --> 00:00:31.168
I controlled it.

7
00:00:31.169 --> 00:00:34.089
I may finally have a way
that I can fight back.

8
00:00:35.840 --> 00:00:38.550
Her heart rate is
19 beats per minute.

9
00:00:38.551 --> 00:00:39.843
That's impossible.

10
00:00:39.844 --> 00:00:41.887
Fatima shouldn't even
be alive right now.

11
00:00:41.888 --> 00:00:43.847
[equipment beeping OS]

12
00:00:43.848 --> 00:00:44.890
Do you want to stay here. Henry?

13
00:00:44.891 --> 00:00:46.976
Yes. yes.

14
00:00:46.977 --> 00:00:49.728
You have to forcibly disconnect.

15
00:00:49.729 --> 00:00:51.981
You have to
eliminate the anchor.

16
00:00:51.982 --> 00:00:55.567
So. the doctor wants me to
eliminate you. To kill you? No.

17
00:00:55.568 --> 00:00:56.902
He's not real.

18
00:00:56.903 --> 00:00:59.863
How could I?
Even if... even if I wanted to.

19
00:00:59.864 --> 00:01:01.782
The dream is gonna provide you
with everything that you need.

20
00:01:01.783 --> 00:01:03.450
You just need to accept
it isn't real.

21
00:01:03.451 --> 00:01:04.702
How can I do that?!

22
00:01:04.703 --> 00:01:05.662
[gasps]

23
00:01:07.205 --> 00:01:08.623
[Sophia]
Do you know who I really am?

24
00:01:11.251 --> 00:01:12.835
[Elgin]
The girl in the background.

25
00:01:12.836 --> 00:01:14.253
she looks just like you.

26
00:01:14.254 --> 00:01:15.797
That's because it is me.

27
00:01:17.716 --> 00:01:20.009
We are standing right above

28
00:01:20.010 --> 00:01:22.344
the cavern those
bones are buried in.

29
00:01:22.345 --> 00:01:24.304
You wanna cut down the tree?

30
00:01:24.305 --> 00:01:25.848
I wanna pull it out
by the roots.

31
00:01:25.849 --> 00:01:29.309
Once you pull out that tree.
it's like opening a window.

32
00:01:29.310 --> 00:01:32.980
Talismans or not. those things
are coming inside.

33
00:01:32.981 --> 00:01:35.899
Whoever's in that tunnel
is gonna get slaughtered.

34
00:01:35.900 --> 00:01:37.776
Once the bones
are out of the ground.

35
00:01:37.777 --> 00:01:39.653
they'll keep the chamber safe.

36
00:01:39.654 --> 00:01:41.155
And then. we get 'em out
with the ladder

37
00:01:41.156 --> 00:01:44.950
that they're putting
together at the. uh. diner.

38
00:01:44.951 --> 00:01:46.493
The Bottle Tree.
are you pulling it down?

39
00:01:46.494 --> 00:01:48.495
We need to make sure
that we can get our people

40
00:01:48.496 --> 00:01:49.580
out of the tunnels safely.

41
00:01:49.581 --> 00:01:51.498
No! You... You can't do this.

42
00:01:51.499 --> 00:01:52.958
You can't!

43
00:01:52.959 --> 00:01:54.501
I'm gonna stop you!

44
00:01:54.502 --> 00:01:58.005
No! No! No!
I am trying to help you!

45
00:01:58.006 --> 00:01:59.715
- [Boyd] I know!
- I'm trying to help!

46
00:01:59.716 --> 00:02:01.383
It needs to be only me and Jade.

47
00:02:01.384 --> 00:02:02.718
- What?
- We're the ones

48
00:02:02.719 --> 00:02:04.428
who failed to save
those children.

49
00:02:04.429 --> 00:02:05.471
Look at the talisman.

50
00:02:05.472 --> 00:02:07.097
Who do you think
those people are?

51
00:02:07.098 --> 00:02:09.266
We only get to do this once.

52
00:02:09.267 --> 00:02:11.310
And I think here. in this place.

53
00:02:11.311 --> 00:02:13.854
the way that we do this matters.

54
00:02:13.855 --> 00:02:15.314
They're in the chamber.

55
00:02:15.315 --> 00:02:16.732
Let's get that truck
into position.

56
00:02:16.733 --> 00:02:18.025
On the next signal. we go.

57
00:02:18.026 --> 00:02:19.568
[Jade straining]

58
00:02:19.569 --> 00:02:20.862
[gasps] Oh. Jesus.

59
00:02:25.325 --> 00:02:26.409
Jade...

60
00:02:28.119 --> 00:02:30.330
[creature] You know. you really
shouldn't be doing that.

61
00:02:33.541 --> 00:02:35.918
[Jade] No. no. Tabitha.

62
00:02:35.919 --> 00:02:37.336
Hey. stay with me.

63
00:02:37.337 --> 00:02:38.379
We're almost there.

64
00:02:40.090 --> 00:02:40.882
[breathing deeply]

65
00:02:43.134 --> 00:02:44.593
Tabitha?

66
00:02:44.594 --> 00:02:45.720
Here.

67
00:02:47.388 --> 00:02:51.392
Come on. come on.
come on. come on. Come on.

68
00:02:53.103 --> 00:02:54.520
Dad?

69
00:02:54.521 --> 00:02:57.147
Just give 'em a moment. okay?

70
00:02:57.148 --> 00:02:58.816
It's just they've
been down there a while.

71
00:02:58.817 --> 00:02:59.901
- [Boyd] Just...
- Okay.

72
00:03:03.071 --> 00:03:06.032
[ominous music playing]

73
00:03:17.043 --> 00:03:18.627
Oh. Jesus.

74
00:03:18.628 --> 00:03:19.670
Don't think about what they are.

75
00:03:19.671 --> 00:03:20.712
Just put them in the bag.

76
00:03:20.713 --> 00:03:22.173
Okay.

77
00:03:26.386 --> 00:03:27.928
You guys! Come.
Get the rope ladder ready.

78
00:03:27.929 --> 00:03:29.388
Okay. okay.

79
00:03:29.389 --> 00:03:30.973
That chamber down there
becomes vulnerable

80
00:03:30.974 --> 00:03:33.684
as soon as that
tree starts to give. 'Kay.

81
00:03:33.685 --> 00:03:36.728
What's Plan B
if we can't pull the tree out?

82
00:03:36.729 --> 00:03:37.814
There is no Plan B.

83
00:03:39.440 --> 00:03:43.193
[suspenseful music playing]

84
00:03:43.194 --> 00:03:44.695
We should signal them
to pull the tree.

85
00:03:44.696 --> 00:03:46.029
Not yet.

86
00:03:46.030 --> 00:03:47.031
Why?

87
00:03:48.950 --> 00:03:50.450
Because the second
that rope ladder drops.

88
00:03:50.451 --> 00:03:51.995
you need to be ready
to go up with the bones.

89
00:03:56.583 --> 00:03:57.833
What do you mean?
What are you talking about?

90
00:03:57.834 --> 00:03:59.209
The bones have to go up last!

91
00:03:59.210 --> 00:04:00.669
They're the only thing
protecting the chamber

92
00:04:00.670 --> 00:04:01.628
once the tree is out.

93
00:04:01.629 --> 00:04:02.380
I lied.

94
00:04:04.340 --> 00:04:06.633
There is nothing protecting the
chamber once the tree is out.

95
00:04:06.634 --> 00:04:08.844
These bones won't
stop them from coming in.

96
00:04:08.845 --> 00:04:10.345
What? No. no. you told me...

97
00:04:10.346 --> 00:04:11.597
If Boyd realized it wasn't safe.

98
00:04:11.598 --> 00:04:13.640
he would've scrubbed
the whole thing.

99
00:04:13.641 --> 00:04:15.767
- I couldn't let that happen.
- God damn it. Jade.

100
00:04:15.768 --> 00:04:17.394
You need to finish this.

101
00:04:17.395 --> 00:04:20.147
You need to break
this fucking cycle.

102
00:04:20.148 --> 00:04:23.525
You go up the rope ladder
with both these bags.

103
00:04:23.526 --> 00:04:25.611
I promise you

104
00:04:25.612 --> 00:04:26.820
I will slow them down long
enough for you to get out.

105
00:04:26.821 --> 00:04:28.113
Jade. please don't do this.

106
00:04:28.114 --> 00:04:29.781
- Look...
- No.

107
00:04:29.782 --> 00:04:31.617
Your children
deserve to go home.

108
00:04:31.618 --> 00:04:33.493
[zips bag]

109
00:04:33.494 --> 00:04:34.620
Jade!

110
00:04:34.621 --> 00:04:36.580
No. No. Jade.

111
00:04:36.581 --> 00:04:39.791
No. Please don't do this.
Don't do this!

112
00:04:39.792 --> 00:04:41.586
You know. I'm glad it was you.

113
00:04:43.796 --> 00:04:47.216
If I had to spend all of those
lifetimes with anyone.

114
00:04:47.217 --> 00:04:48.635
I'm glad it was you.

115
00:04:50.136 --> 00:04:52.012
[buzzing]

116
00:04:52.013 --> 00:04:53.764
Hey. that's it!
Start the truck! Go!

117
00:04:53.765 --> 00:04:55.850
Okay! Let's go!

118
00:04:57.518 --> 00:04:58.894
- There has to be another way!
- There isn't!

119
00:04:58.895 --> 00:05:00.897
[engine revving]

120
00:05:03.358 --> 00:05:07.236
[rumbling. dirt crumbling]

121
00:05:07.237 --> 00:05:09.196
[engine revving]

122
00:05:09.197 --> 00:05:11.406
[bottles clanking]

123
00:05:11.407 --> 00:05:15.078
[rumbling. dirt crumbling]

124
00:05:18.581 --> 00:05:20.415
Give it more!

125
00:05:20.416 --> 00:05:22.001
We gotta get
that thing down now! Go!

126
00:05:27.090 --> 00:05:28.382
Oh. Jesus.

127
00:05:28.383 --> 00:05:29.842
[rumbling. dirt crumbling]

128
00:05:34.138 --> 00:05:35.681
- Come on!
- [Boyd] Here we go. Get ready.

129
00:05:35.682 --> 00:05:37.058
- Come on. Come on.
- Come on.

130
00:05:42.230 --> 00:05:44.816
It's nice. all of us
being together again.

131
00:05:47.277 --> 00:05:48.652
[engine revving]

132
00:05:48.653 --> 00:05:52.407
[rumbling. dirt crumbling]

133
00:05:57.704 --> 00:06:00.748
[dirt crumbling]

134
00:06:02.875 --> 00:06:04.543
They can't come
into the light. Jade.

135
00:06:04.544 --> 00:06:06.045
They can't come into the light!

136
00:06:07.547 --> 00:06:10.090
[engine revving]

137
00:06:10.091 --> 00:06:12.342
Wait. Grab that ladder! Come on!

138
00:06:12.343 --> 00:06:13.261
- [Ellis] Let's go!
- [Boyd] Hey!

139
00:06:14.846 --> 00:06:15.929
Tabitha!

140
00:06:15.930 --> 00:06:17.515
Jade!

141
00:06:22.687 --> 00:06:25.564
Tabitha! Jade! You okay?

142
00:06:25.565 --> 00:06:26.982
Jade...

143
00:06:26.983 --> 00:06:28.567
Get that ladder down here!

144
00:06:28.568 --> 00:06:29.652
Yeah! No!

145
00:06:34.532 --> 00:06:36.491
Gimme that! Give it to me!

146
00:06:36.492 --> 00:06:39.786
We're both getting outta here.

147
00:06:39.787 --> 00:06:41.538
That's it. Got it.

148
00:06:41.539 --> 00:06:43.623
- Okay.
- Go. Come on.

149
00:06:43.624 --> 00:06:46.210
One step at a time.
Don't... Don't look down.

150
00:06:48.880 --> 00:06:50.339
[Jade] That's it. Keep going!

151
00:06:50.340 --> 00:06:51.757
[Boyd] Keep climbing! Come on!

152
00:06:51.758 --> 00:06:54.634
You got it! You're right there.

153
00:06:54.635 --> 00:06:55.594
[shouting] Is it secure?

154
00:06:55.595 --> 00:06:57.012
- It's secure.
- You got it?

155
00:06:57.013 --> 00:06:57.971
Right. keep climbing! Come on!

156
00:06:57.972 --> 00:07:00.808
[straining]

157
00:07:07.565 --> 00:07:09.775
[shrieks]

158
00:07:09.776 --> 00:07:11.526
Tabitha. whoa!

159
00:07:11.527 --> 00:07:12.694
Are you okay?

160
00:07:12.695 --> 00:07:14.821
- It's okay.
- Oh. Jade.

161
00:07:14.822 --> 00:07:16.073
It's all right.

162
00:07:16.074 --> 00:07:18.075
No! Hey! You okay?!

163
00:07:18.076 --> 00:07:19.201
Tabitha?!

164
00:07:19.202 --> 00:07:21.661
Hey! Jade!

165
00:07:21.662 --> 00:07:22.663
What the...?

166
00:07:35.635 --> 00:07:37.136
[snarling]

167
00:07:38.888 --> 00:07:40.305
[screeching]

168
00:07:40.306 --> 00:07:42.057
- [Jade] No. no. No.
- Oh. my God!

169
00:07:42.058 --> 00:07:43.642
What the fuck is happening?

170
00:07:43.643 --> 00:07:45.018
Boyd?

171
00:07:45.019 --> 00:07:46.979
I have no...

172
00:07:48.106 --> 00:07:49.189
Oh. no!

173
00:07:49.190 --> 00:07:51.024
No. no! No. no. no!

174
00:07:51.025 --> 00:07:52.317
Oh. my God!

175
00:07:52.318 --> 00:07:53.403
[rumbling]

176
00:08:03.621 --> 00:08:05.247
Oh. my God! [screaming]

177
00:08:05.248 --> 00:08:10.086
[earthquake rumbling]

178
00:08:14.507 --> 00:08:19.387
["Que Sera. Sera (Whatever Will
Be. Will Be)" plays]

179
