<i>♪ When I was just a little boy ♪</i>

180
00:08:29.021 --> 00:08:31.440
<i>♪ I asked my father ♪</i>

181
00:08:31.441 --> 00:08:32.942
<i>♪ "What will I be?" ♪</i>

182
00:08:35.153 --> 00:08:37.612
<i>♪ "Will I be handsome?" ♪</i>

183
00:08:37.613 --> 00:08:40.073
<i>♪ "Will I be rich?" ♪</i>

184
00:08:40.074 --> 00:08:43.952
<i>♪ Here's what he said to me ♪</i>

185
00:08:43.953 --> 00:08:46.831
<i>♪ Que sera sera ♪</i>

186
00:08:48.166 --> 00:08:51.377
<i>♪ Whatever will be will be ♪</i>

187
00:08:53.045 --> 00:08:57.299
<i>♪ The future's not ours to see ♪</i>

188
00:08:57.300 --> 00:08:59.927
<i>♪ Que sera sera ♪</i>

189
00:09:02.305 --> 00:09:05.099
<i>♪ What will be will be ♪</i>

190
00:09:14.734 --> 00:09:19.571
<i>♪ Now I have
children of my own ♪</i>

191
00:09:19.572 --> 00:09:21.990
<i>♪ They ask their father ♪</i>

192
00:09:21.991 --> 00:09:25.702
<i>♪ "What will I be?" ♪</i>

193
00:09:25.703 --> 00:09:28.205
<i>♪ "Will I be pretty?" ♪</i>

194
00:09:28.206 --> 00:09:30.624
<i>♪ "Will I be rich?" ♪</i>

195
00:09:30.625 --> 00:09:32.835
<i>♪ I tell them tenderly ♪</i>

196
00:09:34.504 --> 00:09:37.089
<i>♪ Que sera sera ♪</i>

197
00:09:38.674 --> 00:09:41.844
<i>♪ Whatever will be will be ♪</i>

198
00:09:43.638 --> 00:09:47.724
<i>♪ The future's not ours to see ♪</i>

199
00:09:47.725 --> 00:09:50.061
<i>♪ Que sera sera ♪</i>

200
00:09:52.855 --> 00:09:55.650
<i>♪ What will be will be ♪</i>

201
00:09:57.985 --> 00:10:00.780
<i>♪ Que sera sera ♪</i>

202
00:10:14.794 --> 00:10:19.130
[earthquake rumbling]

203
00:10:19.131 --> 00:10:20.757
Hey! Hey!

204
00:10:20.758 --> 00:10:22.634
Hey!

205
00:10:22.635 --> 00:10:24.678
Let me out! Please!

206
00:10:24.679 --> 00:10:26.596
Please! Please!

207
00:10:26.597 --> 00:10:28.223
Okay. wait. just wait!
Stop! Stop! Stop!

208
00:10:28.224 --> 00:10:29.307
- No!
- Hold...

209
00:10:29.308 --> 00:10:30.392
- No!
- You're safe here!

210
00:10:30.393 --> 00:10:33.019
What is... What's happening?

211
00:10:33.020 --> 00:10:34.187
I know. I know!

212
00:10:34.188 --> 00:10:35.855
I told you not to
pull down the tree!

213
00:10:35.856 --> 00:10:37.232
Why didn't you listen?

214
00:10:37.233 --> 00:10:40.653
[earthquake rumbling]

215
00:10:42.822 --> 00:10:45.156
[screams]

216
00:10:45.157 --> 00:10:48.535
[breathing heavily]
Oh! Oh. Jesus.

217
00:10:48.536 --> 00:10:50.621
Oh. no.

218
00:10:52.498 --> 00:10:55.500
Oh. no. no. No. no. no.

219
00:10:55.501 --> 00:10:56.918
Jade! Jade. over there! Come on.

220
00:10:56.919 --> 00:10:58.336
Son of a bitch!

221
00:10:58.337 --> 00:10:59.713
[Tabitha] Let's go!

222
00:10:59.714 --> 00:11:01.716
Come on. come on. let's go!
Let's go!

223
00:11:08.514 --> 00:11:10.473
Tabitha?! Jade?!

224
00:11:10.474 --> 00:11:12.767
[creature screeching]

225
00:11:12.768 --> 00:11:14.227
We can't be out
in the open like this. man.

226
00:11:14.228 --> 00:11:16.438
Tabitha!

227
00:11:16.439 --> 00:11:17.939
I'm gonna need you to answer.

228
00:11:17.940 --> 00:11:20.358
[creature screeching]

229
00:11:20.359 --> 00:11:24.279
Jade?! Tabitha.
I need you to talk to me!

230
00:11:24.280 --> 00:11:26.489
- Boyd. we gotta go.
- Get the chain from the truck.

231
00:11:26.490 --> 00:11:27.824
- What?
- I'm going down there.

232
00:11:27.825 --> 00:11:29.826
- You can't go down there.
- Get the fucking chain!

233
00:11:29.827 --> 00:11:31.578
- No!
- No. no. we need to go.

234
00:11:31.579 --> 00:11:32.996
- Please. we need to go now!
- Boyd!

235
00:11:32.997 --> 00:11:34.873
I am not losing them.

236
00:11:34.874 --> 00:11:36.750
If we don't leave now.
we're gonna lose everybody.

237
00:11:36.751 --> 00:11:37.959
[creature screeching]

238
00:11:37.960 --> 00:11:40.003
[creatures screeching]

239
00:11:40.004 --> 00:11:41.212
- Dad!
- We gotta go!

240
00:11:41.213 --> 00:11:44.382
- Boyd!
- [creatures screeching]

241
00:11:44.383 --> 00:11:45.259
[creatures screeching]

242
00:11:49.305 --> 00:11:50.680
[Ellis] Dad?

243
00:11:50.681 --> 00:11:51.598
- [Boyd] Fuck!
- Boyd!

244
00:11:51.599 --> 00:11:52.766
Dad!

245
00:11:52.767 --> 00:11:54.392
Everybody into
the vehicles! Now!

246
00:11:54.393 --> 00:11:57.520
Go. go. go. come on! Go!
All right. let's go!

247
00:11:57.521 --> 00:11:59.481
Randall. help me get
the chain off the truck!

248
00:11:59.482 --> 00:12:01.274
- Come on!
- [hyperventilating]

249
00:12:01.275 --> 00:12:03.485
[indistinct shouting]

250
00:12:03.486 --> 00:12:04.694
[Acosta] Get in the van now!

251
00:12:04.695 --> 00:12:06.780
It's okay. it's okay!

252
00:12:06.781 --> 00:12:07.989
It's okay. Patty! Patty!

253
00:12:07.990 --> 00:12:08.866
- No!
- [shot firing]

254
00:12:10.409 --> 00:12:12.535
- Get in!
- [Acosta] Boyd. come on!

255
00:12:12.536 --> 00:12:15.121
- [shots firing]
- In! Let's go! Come on!

256
00:12:15.122 --> 00:12:16.456
[Acosta] Kristi! Let's go!

257
00:12:16.457 --> 00:12:17.874
- Come on...
- Get in!

258
00:12:17.875 --> 00:12:19.834
