I don't...

531
00:26:47.619 --> 00:26:49.578
Okay. okay.

532
00:26:49.579 --> 00:26:50.663
[sobbing]

533
00:26:50.664 --> 00:26:52.122
Okay. we'll be okay.

534
00:26:52.123 --> 00:26:54.792
[sobbing]

535
00:26:54.793 --> 00:26:55.961
I'm right here.

536
00:26:57.379 --> 00:26:58.505
I'm right here.

537
00:27:00.131 --> 00:27:02.508
[wailing]

538
00:27:02.509 --> 00:27:04.468
I'm right here.

539
00:27:04.469 --> 00:27:06.805
[wailing]

540
00:27:09.849 --> 00:27:11.767
Okay.

541
00:27:11.768 --> 00:27:13.645
[wailing]

542
00:27:15.981 --> 00:27:18.483
[muffled wailing]

543
00:27:33.582 --> 00:27:34.665
[deafening thunder claps]

544
00:27:34.666 --> 00:27:36.125
Jesus!

545
00:27:36.126 --> 00:27:38.211
[deafening thunder claps]

546
00:27:40.380 --> 00:27:42.090
[thunder continues crashing]

547
00:27:57.105 --> 00:27:59.024
[thunder crashing]

548
00:28:11.911 --> 00:28:16.665
[thunder crashing]

549
00:28:16.666 --> 00:28:19.668
What the fuck did we do?

550
00:28:19.669 --> 00:28:21.296
[thunder continues crashing]

551
00:28:24.049 --> 00:28:25.425
[thunder rumbling]

552
00:28:27.719 --> 00:28:29.512
[car approaching]

553
00:28:34.142 --> 00:28:36.393
They're back!

554
00:28:36.394 --> 00:28:38.730
No. no. no. no. no!
Stay on the porch!

555
00:28:55.038 --> 00:28:56.997
Get her inside. Where's Tabitha?

556
00:28:56.998 --> 00:29:00.209
We didn't get a signal.
I don't know where they are.

557
00:29:00.210 --> 00:29:01.711
Where's Mom?

558
00:29:08.760 --> 00:29:09.802
[breathing shakily]

559
00:29:09.803 --> 00:29:11.262
Julie?

560
00:29:14.766 --> 00:29:16.601
I don't...

561
00:29:18.978 --> 00:29:21.647
Ethan... Ethan. please!

562
00:29:21.648 --> 00:29:24.317
[ominous music playing]

563
00:29:51.928 --> 00:29:53.263
Boyd?

564
00:29:58.810 --> 00:30:00.061
Kenny?

565
00:30:02.439 --> 00:30:04.023
Victor?

566
00:30:26.755 --> 00:30:29.924
[breathing unsteadily]

567
00:30:37.015 --> 00:30:38.474
- [door opens]
- [Kenny] Henry.

568
00:30:38.475 --> 00:30:39.725
Hey.

569
00:30:39.726 --> 00:30:41.226
Did you need something?

570
00:30:41.227 --> 00:30:43.103
No. I was just. uh.
looking for Victor.

571
00:30:43.104 --> 00:30:46.231
Did you see the lightning?

572
00:30:46.232 --> 00:30:47.858
Yeah. it was kinda hard to miss.

573
00:30:47.859 --> 00:30:49.694
I gotta go. Sorry. Uh. see ya.

574
00:30:50.862 --> 00:30:51.780
[door opens]

575
00:31:01.289 --> 00:31:03.166
She's not coming back. is she?

576
00:31:07.003 --> 00:31:08.338
Ethan...

577
00:31:09.881 --> 00:31:11.256
your mom and
Jade were still in the...

578
00:31:11.257 --> 00:31:15.344
[slamming]

579
00:31:15.345 --> 00:31:17.095
It's happening again!

580
00:31:17.096 --> 00:31:20.474
[slamming]

581
00:31:20.475 --> 00:31:24.645
[glass shattering]

582
00:31:24.646 --> 00:31:27.022
Ethan... Okay. Go. go. go. go!

583
00:31:27.023 --> 00:31:28.273
Ethan!

584
00:31:28.274 --> 00:31:29.651
No! Ethan!

585
00:31:33.112 --> 00:31:34.488
Ethan. stop.

586
00:31:34.489 --> 00:31:36.448
No! Mom promised
she'd come back! She promised!

587
00:31:36.449 --> 00:31:37.658
I know. I know.

588
00:31:37.659 --> 00:31:39.785
She said she was
gonna get us home!

589
00:31:39.786 --> 00:31:41.203
And now. she's gone!

590
00:31:41.204 --> 00:31:43.038
And Dad's gone.
And soon you'll be gone!

591
00:31:43.039 --> 00:31:45.123
No. no. no!

592
00:31:45.124 --> 00:31:48.502
Everyone here is gonna die.
and I'm gonna be here alone!

593
00:31:48.503 --> 00:31:49.503
- But I can't...
- No!

594
00:31:49.504 --> 00:31:50.921
I don't want to!

595
00:31:50.922 --> 00:31:52.548
No. you are not
going to be alone!

596
00:31:52.549 --> 00:31:54.132
You will never be alone. Ethan!

597
00:31:54.133 --> 00:31:55.592
You're lying!
That's what she said!

598
00:31:55.593 --> 00:31:57.427
I can't...

599
00:31:57.428 --> 00:31:59.555
[Julie] Listen to me. Listen.

600
00:31:59.556 --> 00:32:02.391
We are gonna look out
for each other. okay?

601
00:32:02.392 --> 00:32:04.394
You and me. we're gonna
take care of each other.

602
00:32:05.478 --> 00:32:06.396
How?

603
00:32:10.775 --> 00:32:11.901
I don't know.

604
00:32:14.487 --> 00:32:16.238
But we're gonna
figure it out together.

605
00:32:16.239 --> 00:32:17.782
Okay?

606
00:32:19.576 --> 00:32:23.120
Okay. Come here.

607
00:32:23.121 --> 00:32:23.997
[sobbing]

608
00:32:42.056 --> 00:32:44.559
Hey.

609
00:32:48.062 --> 00:32:50.564
Not the kind day
we hoped for. was it?

610
00:32:50.565 --> 00:32:52.190
Victor was right.

611
00:32:52.191 --> 00:32:55.110
We never should
have pulled that tree.

612
00:32:55.111 --> 00:32:57.279
What are we gonna do now?

613
00:32:57.280 --> 00:32:58.530
[Boyd] I don't know.

614
00:32:58.531 --> 00:32:59.532
Boyd?

615
00:33:03.786 --> 00:33:05.287
We need to go back.

616
00:33:05.288 --> 00:33:06.496
What?

617
00:33:06.497 --> 00:33:07.497
The bones are still down there.

618
00:33:07.498 --> 00:33:08.832
- Look. we can't...
- No. no. no.

619
00:33:08.833 --> 00:33:10.167
You told people that those bones

620
00:33:10.168 --> 00:33:12.336
were the key to
getting us outta here.

621
00:33:12.337 --> 00:33:13.837
We can't just stop now.
We have to go back and get them.

622
00:33:13.838 --> 00:33:15.130
And... And do what?

623
00:33:15.131 --> 00:33:16.548
- Wha...
- Even if we had them.

624
00:33:16.549 --> 00:33:18.675
we don't know how to use them!

625
00:33:18.676 --> 00:33:20.552
The only people who knew
anything about them

626
00:33:20.553 --> 00:33:23.388
went down into those tunnels.
and they didn't come out.

627
00:33:23.389 --> 00:33:25.849
This place got exactly
what it fucking wanted.

628
00:33:25.850 --> 00:33:27.809
Is there any chance
they survived?

629
00:33:27.810 --> 00:33:29.436
How. Kenny?

630
00:33:29.437 --> 00:33:31.063
There's one exit
out of that chamber.

631
00:33:31.064 --> 00:33:34.149
One! If they were alive...

632
00:33:34.150 --> 00:33:36.735
God damn it!

633
00:33:36.736 --> 00:33:38.403
If they were alive.
they'd be here right now.

634
00:33:38.404 --> 00:33:40.447
No. we can't just give up!

635
00:33:40.448 --> 00:33:42.658
All right. then tell me
how to move forward. okay?

636
00:33:42.659 --> 00:33:46.203
Please. Anybody. Tell me!

637
00:33:46.204 --> 00:33:50.248
We just made the sun go down!

638
00:33:50.249 --> 00:33:54.086
We fucking tore a hole in
the goddamn sky with lightning!

639
00:33:54.087 --> 00:33:56.380
Who the fuck
even knows what that means!

640
00:33:56.381 --> 00:33:58.382
So. what are we supposed to do

641
00:33:58.383 --> 00:33:59.675
that could possibly
make anything better?

642
00:33:59.676 --> 00:34:00.884
- [static]
- Boyd...

643
00:34:00.885 --> 00:34:02.511
We lost three people today!
- Boyd...

644
00:34:02.512 --> 00:34:05.430
- I'm not going... What?!
- Boyd! Stop!

645
00:34:05.431 --> 00:34:06.599
- Listen.
- [static beeping]

646
00:34:08.476 --> 00:34:10.978
[static beeping]

647
00:34:10.979 --> 00:34:12.062
Are you...?

648
00:34:12.063 --> 00:34:13.563
[static beeping]

649
00:34:13.564 --> 00:34:15.649
What the...?

650
00:34:15.650 --> 00:34:17.068
[static beeping]

651
00:34:18.861 --> 00:34:21.113
Shit. You see that?

652
00:34:21.114 --> 00:34:24.282
[static beeping]

653
00:34:24.283 --> 00:34:25.534
[static continues beeping]

654
00:34:25.535 --> 00:34:27.285
Come on.

655
00:34:27.286 --> 00:34:29.204
[static beeping]

656
00:34:29.205 --> 00:34:30.498
[power cutting out]

657
00:34:35.586 --> 00:34:37.005
Ahh... fuck!

658
00:34:38.715 --> 00:34:40.716
Fuck.

659
00:34:40.717 --> 00:34:42.427
That's it. The battery's dead.

660
00:34:44.053 --> 00:34:45.096
Do you think it went through?

661
00:34:47.765 --> 00:34:49.766
Even if it did.
they'd still have to find us.

662
00:34:49.767 --> 00:34:50.852
[exhales]

663
00:34:53.104 --> 00:34:55.063
I'm so sorry.
I never should have...

664
00:34:55.064 --> 00:34:56.231
No. no. no. no. no. no. no.

665
00:34:56.232 --> 00:34:57.607
Don't give up.
do you understand?

666
00:34:57.608 --> 00:34:58.609
We're not dying here.

667
00:35:05.992 --> 00:35:07.909
[strains]

668
00:35:07.910 --> 00:35:09.328
[Jade] It won't break.

669
00:35:12.874 --> 00:35:15.042
But we can dig.

670
00:35:15.043 --> 00:35:16.960
We dig until we get under them.

671
00:35:16.961 --> 00:35:18.337
It's worth a shot.

672
00:35:20.423 --> 00:35:21.758
All right.

673
00:35:25.845 --> 00:35:27.721
What you did back there.

674
00:35:27.722 --> 00:35:30.599
what you were willing to do...

675
00:35:30.600 --> 00:35:32.809
I just wanted to say thank you.

676
00:35:32.810 --> 00:35:35.729
Well. you know what they say:

677
00:35:35.730 --> 00:35:37.523
women and children first.

678
00:35:42.028 --> 00:35:42.862
You're welcome.

679
00:36:02.840 --> 00:36:03.925
Okay. here we go.

680
00:36:06.928 --> 00:36:08.929
Okay. come on.

681
00:36:08.930 --> 00:36:10.098
Down. Watch your step.

682
00:36:18.189 --> 00:36:19.064
[Randall] Easy now.

683
00:36:19.065 --> 00:36:20.066
Yeah.

684
00:36:24.821 --> 00:36:25.946
Okay.

685
00:36:25.947 --> 00:36:27.572
Are you gonna be okay?

686
00:36:27.573 --> 00:36:29.574
Yeah. I'll be fine.

687
00:36:29.575 --> 00:36:31.744
All right. Okay.

688
00:36:44.590 --> 00:36:47.843
I'm gonna head down
with her. to the church.

689
00:36:47.844 --> 00:36:49.052
Anything you need.
do you understand?

690
00:36:49.053 --> 00:36:50.138
Yeah.

691
00:37:01.566 --> 00:37:02.649
Come.

692
00:37:02.650 --> 00:37:04.025
Why?

693
00:37:04.026 --> 00:37:05.652
Come. come.

694
00:37:05.653 --> 00:37:07.362
We got a signal.

695
00:37:07.363 --> 00:37:08.655
- What?
- [Fatima] What?

696
00:37:08.656 --> 00:37:13.577
Yeah. from Tabitha
and Jade's radio.

697
00:37:13.578 --> 00:37:15.036
So. they're alive?

698
00:37:15.037 --> 00:37:17.038
I'm going back to find out.

699
00:37:17.039 --> 00:37:18.123
You're going to the tunnels.

700
00:37:18.124 --> 00:37:19.958
- Yeah.
- All right. I'm coming with you.

701
00:37:19.959 --> 00:37:21.459
I'm going by myself.

702
00:37:21.460 --> 00:37:23.336
I'm not risking
anybody else's life today.

703
00:37:23.337 --> 00:37:24.838
No. Dad. what if they're hurt?

704
00:37:24.839 --> 00:37:26.590
I mean. how are you gonna
carry both of them by yourself?

705
00:37:26.591 --> 00:37:28.550
- I'll figure it out.
- Are you sure that signal

706
00:37:28.551 --> 00:37:29.968
even came from Jade and Tabitha?

707
00:37:29.969 --> 00:37:32.429
Exactly. look. I mean. these
things are smart. Dad. okay?

708
00:37:32.430 --> 00:37:34.431
What if they're just trying to
bait you out there?

709
00:37:34.432 --> 00:37:36.558
- I'm going with you.
- We're both going.

710
00:37:36.559 --> 00:37:37.767
All right.
let's just everybody...

711
00:37:37.768 --> 00:37:40.729
No. Boyd. I can feel
them when they're close.

712
00:37:40.730 --> 00:37:42.939
What?

713
00:37:42.940 --> 00:37:45.067
I knew that thing
was coming to the clinic.

714
00:37:47.612 --> 00:37:50.572
I sensed it
before we saw it. If I'm...

715
00:37:50.573 --> 00:37:52.742
if I'm down there with you.
then maybe I can warn you.

716
00:37:54.827 --> 00:37:57.538
[ominous music playing]

717
00:38:09.592 --> 00:38:10.843
Hello?

718
00:38:12.303 --> 00:38:14.055
Is anyone here?

719
00:38:16.432 --> 00:38:19.435
[ominous music playing]

720
00:38:42.208 --> 00:38:44.542
[knocking]

721
00:38:44.543 --> 00:38:46.670
[Victor] Dad?

722
00:38:46.671 --> 00:38:48.171
Are you in there?

723
00:38:48.172 --> 00:38:48.965
Yeah.

724
00:38:54.262 --> 00:38:57.014
Hey. Today was scary.

725
00:38:58.557 --> 00:38:59.891
Yes.

726
00:38:59.892 --> 00:39:01.394
Nothing like that
ever happened before.

727
00:39:03.521 --> 00:39:05.314
Why are you sitting
in here all alone?

728
00:39:10.903 --> 00:39:12.446
I'm just... thinking.

729
00:39:20.121 --> 00:39:21.872
Did I do something wrong?

730
00:39:24.208 --> 00:39:24.917
What?

731
00:39:32.341 --> 00:39:35.011
You were different before.
You were happy.

732
00:39:36.762 --> 00:39:40.181
We dragged a bed in here.
so that we could be roommates.

733
00:39:40.182 --> 00:39:42.100
Yeah.

734
00:39:42.101 --> 00:39:45.855
And then. I told you
about the man in yellow.

735
00:39:48.399 --> 00:39:50.526
I showed you
that picture. and I...

736
00:39:52.403 --> 00:39:53.611
I ruined it.

737
00:39:53.612 --> 00:39:54.655
No.

738
00:39:56.198 --> 00:39:59.535
Son. you... you didn't ruin it.

739
00:40:02.246 --> 00:40:03.830
[exhales]

740
00:40:03.831 --> 00:40:05.666
The problem is...

741
00:40:07.501 --> 00:40:10.087
...it was never real.

742
00:40:13.549 --> 00:40:15.092
Why do you have that?

743
00:40:18.012 --> 00:40:22.767
I've seen what's real.
Victor. and I need to go back.

744
00:40:23.976 --> 00:40:28.188
You begged me to come back.

745
00:40:28.189 --> 00:40:29.690
You have a son.

746
00:40:31.275 --> 00:40:33.276
Victor. you were happy.

747
00:40:33.277 --> 00:40:35.028
Dad...

748
00:40:35.029 --> 00:40:36.821
Dad. something
here's lied to you.

749
00:40:36.822 --> 00:40:39.032
I've been lying to myself.

750
00:40:39.033 --> 00:40:40.116
- Dad!
- All of these years...

751
00:40:40.117 --> 00:40:41.994
- Dad. please!
- It's time to stop.

752
00:40:44.455 --> 00:40:45.622
I'm so sorry.

753
00:40:45.623 --> 00:40:46.624
[Ethan] Victor!

754
00:40:48.000 --> 00:40:49.584
- What?
- No! Run!

755
00:40:49.585 --> 00:40:51.336
[grunting]

756
00:40:51.337 --> 00:40:53.088
Why are you doing this?!

757
00:40:53.089 --> 00:40:54.631
You said that we'd be okay!

758
00:40:54.632 --> 00:40:57.092
You said that you
would protect me!

759
00:40:57.093 --> 00:40:59.886
Why did you
come here and do this?!

760
00:40:59.887 --> 00:41:02.597
- I'm sorr...
- Why?!

761
00:41:02.598 --> 00:41:04.392
Why?!

762
00:41:20.032 --> 00:41:24.787
[ominous music playing]

763
00:41:39.093 --> 00:41:40.761
Did you get them?

764
00:41:42.596 --> 00:41:44.722
[bag clacking]

765
00:41:44.723 --> 00:41:46.559
Good girl.

766
00:41:51.272 --> 00:41:54.733
[ominous music playing]

767
00:42:04.743 --> 00:42:05.661
[Boyd] Okay.

768
00:42:07.204 --> 00:42:08.538
All right.
So. how does this work?

769
00:42:08.539 --> 00:42:09.874
I'm not sure.

770
00:42:11.542 --> 00:42:14.085
It's a little
different every time.

771
00:42:14.086 --> 00:42:16.212
Okay. well. let's just
all stay close together.

772
00:42:16.213 --> 00:42:19.299
If anything goes wrong down
there. anything.

773
00:42:19.300 --> 00:42:22.677
you two run. You understand me?

774
00:42:22.678 --> 00:42:24.304
No questions. no arguments.

775
00:42:24.305 --> 00:42:26.014
Promise me.

776
00:42:26.015 --> 00:42:27.600
Promise.

777
00:42:29.435 --> 00:42:30.603
You?

778
00:42:33.564 --> 00:42:34.607
Okay.

779
00:42:35.858 --> 00:42:37.026
Hey.

780
00:42:38.152 --> 00:42:39.277
All right.

781
00:42:39.278 --> 00:42:41.946
[exhaling sharply]

782
00:42:41.947 --> 00:42:44.617
[foreboding music playing]

783
00:42:49.330 --> 00:42:51.539
Fuck. We can't do this
with our hands.

784
00:42:51.540 --> 00:42:53.750
We need those goddamn shovels.

785
00:42:53.751 --> 00:42:56.336
[breathing heavily]
We use the bones.

786
00:42:56.337 --> 00:42:57.879
What?

787
00:42:57.880 --> 00:43:01.174
Yeah. to dig.
we can use the bones.

788
00:43:01.175 --> 00:43:02.760
If we don't move these bars.
we're gonna die here.

789
00:43:12.061 --> 00:43:15.564
[foreboding music playing]

790
00:43:25.407 --> 00:43:27.034
Stop! Stop.

791
00:43:32.373 --> 00:43:34.416
[creature screeching
in distance]

792
00:43:48.639 --> 00:43:50.432
All right. Come on.

793
00:44:00.859 --> 00:44:03.445
It's hard to
believe this is real.

794
00:44:05.573 --> 00:44:07.824
that these bones were
actually children once.

795
00:44:07.825 --> 00:44:09.534
and that we were...

796
00:44:09.535 --> 00:44:11.078
I know. I know. I know.

797
00:44:27.511 --> 00:44:30.055
[mournful music playing]

798
00:44:53.495 --> 00:44:55.038
[gasps]

799
00:44:55.039 --> 00:44:56.790
This was her.

800
00:44:58.709 --> 00:45:00.418
This was her.

801
00:45:00.419 --> 00:45:01.712
This was her!

802
00:45:04.381 --> 00:45:06.382
[creatures screeching
in distance]

803
00:45:06.383 --> 00:45:07.926
Oh. fuck.

804
00:45:10.763 --> 00:45:13.682
[creatures
screeching in distance]

